{"content": "I need to multiply 41a \u00d7 849 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 41a (base 11) to base 10**\n- 41a = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 10\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 10\u00d71\n- = 484 + 11 + 10\n- = 505\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 849 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 849 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 9\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 9\u00d71\n- = 968 + 44 + 9\n- = 1021\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 505 \u00d7 1021 = 515,605\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 515,605 back to base 11**\n- 515,605 \u00f7 11 = 46,873 R 2\n- 46,873 \u00f7 11 = 4,261 R 2\n- 4,261 \u00f7 11 = 387 R 4\n- 387 \u00f7 11 = 35 R 2\n- 35 \u00f7 11 = 3 R 2\n- 3 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 3\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 322422\n\n**Answer: 322422**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 390}